- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category for the same reason as above. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the practical application of the proposed technique for end-users. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the time and computation complexity of the proposed technique and suggests approximation techniques to improve it.
